    <body>
        <p>If you have a content file open and want to quickly find where it is stored in the Content Explorer, you can right-click the file and select <span class="Emphasis">Locate in Explorer</span>. You can also open the <span class="Emphasis">Project</span> ribbon and click <span class="Emphasis">Locate in Explorer</span>. Flare opens the Content Explorer, expanding folders to show where the file is located.</p>
    </body>
</html>